      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 19.3 - 老子 19.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 19.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>絕仁棄義，民復孝慈；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If we could renounce our benevolence and discard our righteousness, the people would again become filial and kindly.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
